requirement.en: Send 1 Beast or Warrior Type monster with 200 DEF from your hand to the Graveyard.

effect.en: Draw 1 card. Also, if you sent a Normal Monster to the Graveyard to meet the requirement, this face-up card can be treated as 2 Tributes for the Tribute Summon of a monster with 200 DEF in Attack Position this turn.
